  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "chapterTitle": "第一卷 蛮族之入侵及基督教会之事业",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "27326044_5_1453-1523",
          "range": "1453-1523",
          "rangeStart": 1453,
          "rangeEnd": 1523,
          "markText": "吾人研究过去之人事，断不可心存藐视，以荒谬目之，须平心静气，具有同情。盖史家之目的，不在批评过去制度之当否，而在说明过去制度之由来及其变化。",
          "colorStyle": 5,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1739857233,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-02-18 13:40:33",
          "chapterUid": 5,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1453&rangeEnd=1523",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1453&rangeEnd=1523"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_5_1453-1523",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1453-1523",
      "markText": "吾人研究过去之人事，断不可心存藐视，以荒谬目之，须平心静气，具有同情。盖史家之目的，不在批评过去制度之当否，而在说明过去制度之由来及其变化。",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1453&rangeEnd=1523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1453&rangeEnd=1523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_6_1227-1323",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1227-1323",
      "markText": "视甚密。罗马政府除维持秩序，管理司法，防守边疆外，尚有管理民食之责任。有时且迫国民之子继其父之业，不得见异而思迁。贫民之饮食，由政府供给之，故无蠢动之患。此外并费巨款举行赛车格斗诸戏以娱国民。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1323",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1323"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_3_496-542",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "496-542",
      "markText": "我国人研究西洋历史的道路，凡有两条，一是读西洋历史名著的原本，一是读中国人自己的编著或译本。",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=496&rangeEnd=542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=496&rangeEnd=542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_6_620-672",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "620-672",
      "markText": "至于今日之德国，在当日则草莱未辟，蛮族居之。罗马人曾欲力征之而不得，乃沿莱茵及多瑙河两河筑垒驻兵以御之。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=620&rangeEnd=672",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=620&rangeEnd=672"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_6_998-1016",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "998-1016",
      "markText": "（二）罗马人民之尊崇皇帝，几同神圣。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=998&rangeEnd=1016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=998&rangeEnd=1016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_6_1799-1832",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1799-1832",
      "markText": "罗马国内之大道，四通八达，邮传军队，朝发夕至。商民行旅，来往无虞。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1799&rangeEnd=1832",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1799&rangeEnd=1832"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_3_1122-1168",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1122-1168",
      "markText": "欧美人所著的历史，在我们东方人用世界的眼光看来，有许多是累赘可删的，有许多是应当增加材料的。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1122&rangeEnd=1168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1122&rangeEnd=1168"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_5_1613-1661",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1613-1661",
      "markText": "故本书所述之中古欧洲史，始终以同情贯彻其间，不作诛心之论，盖过去制度之得以存在，必皆有优点者也。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1613&rangeEnd=1661",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1613&rangeEnd=1661"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_3_955-1008",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "955-1008",
      "markText": "第一，历史的著作，大抵是偏于学术的，所以它定不能得到群众的狂热欢迎，因此，人们或因得不到相当的报酬而气馁。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=955&rangeEnd=1008",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=955&rangeEnd=1008"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_9_2875-2885",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2875-2885",
      "markText": "修道士所居之处曰寺。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27326044&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2875&rangeEnd=2885",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c7232ec071a0f65cc722182?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2875&rangeEnd=2885"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27326044_6_1627-1701",
